For a similar types of weapons, see banner and polearm.
"Mycelium" and "Mushtree" redirect here. For the fossil enrichment pool, see Mycelium pool. For the scenery object, see Mushtree (scenery)
This guide is the expansion of all subquests of Recipe for Disaster.
The Toxic trident (e) is the uncharged version of this item and becomes Trident of the swamp (e) when charged.
Note that certain items called "banner" are in fact categorised as polestaves, which are not to be confused with polearms.
